  "detailed_description": "Concept 20 consist of the following gameplays.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Controlling only the ball you will jump your way into the yellow box.<br />\r\n- With the help of a flat bar, you will pick up the ball and try to traverse through all obstacles.<br />\r\n- With the help of numbered blocks you will must figure out a way to get to the yellow box.<br />\r\n- With 10 bars you will designs a path through various obstacles to complete the level.",
